OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start.
OL,6,FCloud will increase this morning, with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of mainly light rain
OL,8,Freaching the Pennines around mid-
OL,9,Fafternoon and then spreading east all
OL,10,Fareas by early evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will clear east
OL,13,Fovernight with mostly dry conditions
OL,14,Fand clear spells following, although a
OL,15,Ffew showers are likely to arrive
OL,16,Facross the Pennines.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
