OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSunny spells and isolated
OL,6,Fshowers, these most likely across the
OL,7,FPennines, until late afternoon. Then
OL,8,Ffrequent showers will spread east,
OL,9,Flocally heavy with a small chance of
OL,10,Fhail and thunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fsunshine and isolated showers. Rain
OL,14,Fand strong winds arrive overnight.
OL,15,FTuesday breezy with frequent heavy
OL,16,Fshowers. Wednesday breezy with showers
OL,17,For longer spells of rain, but
OL,18,Ftemperatures near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
